<paragraph id="IFRS15_IE39" base="F31740176"><paranum>IE39</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="IE39"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0954">The entity determines that the input measure, on the basis of costs incurred, provides an appropriate measure of progress towards complete satisfaction of the performance obligation. By the end of the first year, the entity has satisfied 60 per cent of its performance obligation on the basis of costs incurred to date (CU420,000) relative to total expected costs (CU700,000). The entity reassesses the variable consideration and concludes that the amount is still constrained in accordance with <xref id="IFRS15_X1166" base="F33216804" href="IFRS15_56.dita#IFRS15_56">paragraphs 56&#x2013;58 of IFRS 15</xref>. Consequently, the cumulative revenue and costs recognised for the first year are as follows:</p><table id="IFRS15_TAB0003" base="SL31740232" frame="none" orient="port"><tgroup cols="3"><colspec colnum="1" colname="C1" colwidth="30*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="2" colname="C2" colwidth="15*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><colspec colnum="3" colname="C3" colwidth="55*" colsep="0" rowsep="0" align="left"/><tbody><row keep_together="3"><entry colname="C1"> <p id="IFRS15_P0955" typeface="sansserif"/></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0956" typeface="sansserif"><b>CU</b></p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0957" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0958" typeface="sansserif">Revenue</p></entry><entry colname="C2" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0959" typeface="sansserif">600,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0960" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0961" typeface="sansserif">Costs</p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0962" typeface="sansserif">420,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0963" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row><row><entry colname="C1" align="left" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0964" typeface="sansserif">Gross profit</p></entry><entry colname="C2" rowsep="1" double_underline="yes" align="right" valign="bottom"> <p id="IFRS15_P0965" typeface="sansserif">180,000</p></entry><entry colname="C3"> <p id="IFRS15_P0966" typeface="sansserif"/></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>